Text: There may be better apps around for scanning but for me Clear Scan works well and reliably. Enough functions to collect an image, crop it, file and collate it, and save it (JPG or PDF), without being overwhelmed or underwhelmed with options. I keep using it. For me that's the test. Best feature: its autocropping function. The cropping lines auto placement is not always where you want but you can shift them before the actual cropping without any difficulty. This app works well for OCR too.
